<div class="ugc-mod reading-notes">
  <div class="hd">
    <h2>
      读书笔记&nbsp;&nbsp;· · · · · ·&nbsp;
          <span class="pl">(<a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/26652938/annotation">共<span property="v:count">5</span>篇</a>)</span>

    </h2>

      <a class="redbutt rr j a_show_login" href="https://www.douban.com/register?reason=annotate" rel="nofollow"><span>我来写笔记</span></a>
  </div>
  

    <div class="bd">
      <ul class="inline-tabs">
        <li class="on"><a href="#rank" id="by_rank" >按有用程度</a></li>
        <li><a href="#page" id="by_page" >按页码先后</a></li>
        <li><a href="#time" id="by_time" >最新笔记</a></li>
      </ul>
      
  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="37983541">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/8604754/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u8604754-11.jpg" alt="铁柱" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37983541/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37983541/" class="">第282页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/8604754/" class=" " title="铁柱">铁柱</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37983541">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">通常认为日美战争是一场围绕争夺中国市场的战争，但是这种说法并不准确，实际上，它是围绕英国及其殖民地的命运走向而发动的一场战争。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-06-17 14:34</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                通常认为日美战争是一场围绕争夺中国市场的战争，但是这种说法并不准确，实际上，它是围绕英国及其殖民地的命运走向而发动的一场战争。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







